'''FileHippo''' is an [[Internet]] [[download]] [[website]] that offers [[open source]], [[freeware]], and [[shareware]] programs for Windows. It does not accept user uploaded files.<ref>[http://www.filehippo.com/info/about/ About] FileHippo.com</ref> The website also offers its own software, FileHippo Update Checker, a free program that scans a computer and then reports out-dated software in a web-page, offering links to updated versions.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.filehippo.com/updatechecker|title=Update Checker|publisher=FileHippo|accessdate=2011-03-31}}</ref>
According to [[Quantcast]], FileHippo receives more than three million [[USA|US]] visitors each month and [[Alexa Internet|Alexa]] lists FileHippo among the 1000 most visited websites worldwide.<ref name=alexa>[http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/www.filehippo.com Filehippo.com Site Info:], Alexa</ref>
